All right, enough is enough.  I'm not opposed to elections, but these are 
excessive OOC's.  The election will be announced when the Council figures out 
who is running, then each candidate will be allowed ONE post to give reasons 
they should be elected.  Until that time it'd be nice if we could concentrate 
on the game.

--part1_18d.a93ff93.2a60751c_boundary
